#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Directory Filter"
msgstr "filter fascikli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is controlled by <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Show Filter Bar</guisubmenu></menuchoice> and allows you "
"to choose which types of item are displayed in a folder."
msgstr ""
"Ovim upravljate preko <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>Shift</keycap><keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Alatke</guimenu><guisubmenu>Filterska traka</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>, gde možete izabrati po tipu stavke koje se prikazuju u fascikli."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2054
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Gallery"
msgstr "galerija slika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2055
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In File Manager mode, you can select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Create Image Gallery</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or use "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> to create an HTML page with "
"thumbnails of all the images in the current folder. By default the HTML page "
"is called <filename>images.html</filename> and the thumbnails are put into a "
"new <filename>images</filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"U režimu menadžera fajlova, možete odabrati <menuchoice><guimenu>Alatke</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Napravi galeriju slika...</guisubmenu></menuchoice> (ili "
"pritisnuti <keycombo><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>I</keycap></keycombo>) da "
"stvorite HTML stranicu sa sličicama za sve slike u tekućoj fascikli. "
"Podrazumevano ime HTML stranice je <filename>images.html</filename>, a "
"sličice se stavljaju u novu fasciklu <filename>images</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2061
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start the Image Gallery plugin a dialog opens allowing you to "
"adjust the way the gallery is created."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete priključak za galeriju slika, pojaviće se dijalog u kome "
"podešavate način stvaranja galerije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2065
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page Look"
msgstr "Izgled stranice"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2067
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Look dialog is for adjusting the appearance of the gallery page."
msgstr "Ovaj dijalog služi za podešavanje izgleda stranice galerije."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look Dialog Screenshot"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana dijaloga za izgled."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:2077 index.docbook:2148 index.docbook:2200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2085
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page title"
msgstr "Naslov stranice:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2086
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Page title option has a text input box for changing the title of the "
"image gallery page."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija daje polje u koje unosite željeni naslov stranice sa galerijom "
"slika."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Images per row"
msgstr "Slikâ po vrsti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Images per row option has a slider and a spin box for adjusting the "
"number of thumbnails that are in a single row in the gallery."
msgstr ""
"Ovu opciju čini klizač i brojčanik kojim podešavate broj sličica po jednoj "
"vrsti u galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2095
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show image file name"
msgstr "Prikaži ime fajla slike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Show image file name check box allows you to choose whether to display "
"filenames below the gallery thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"Ovom kućicom određujete da li se vide imena fajlova ispod sličica u galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show image file size"
msgstr "Prikaži veličinu fajla slike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Show image filesize check box allows you to choose whether to display "
"filesizes below the gallery thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"Ovom kućicom određujete da li se vide veličine fajlova ispod sličica u "
"galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show image dimensions"
msgstr "Prikaži dimenzije slike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Show image dimensions check box allows you to choose whether to display "
"image dimensions in pixels below the gallery thumbnails."
msgstr ""
"Ovom kućicom određujete da li se vide dimenzije slika ispod sličica u "
"galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font name"
msgstr "Ime fonta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Font name combo box provides you with a choice of which font to use in "
"creating the gallery."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj padajući spisak omogućava biranje fonta koji se koristi za ispis tekst "
"u galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font size"
msgstr "Veličina fonta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Font size spin box is for changing the size of the font you selected."
msgstr "Ovim brojčanikom menjate veličinu izabranog fonta."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Foreground color"
msgstr "Boja ispisa:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Foreground color option has a selector for choosing the foreground color "
"of the gallery, this includes the text areas."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija daje birač boje ispisa u galeriji, pod koju spadaju sve zone sa "
"tekstom."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background color"
msgstr "Boja pozadine:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Background color option has a selector for choosing the background color "
"of the gallery."
msgstr "Ova opcija daje birač boje pozadine u galeriji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Fascikle"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Folders dialog is used for choosing where to save the gallery. This "
"dialog is also used to configure which folders are used."
msgstr ""
"Kroz dijalog fascikli birate gde će galerija biti sačuvana. Ovde takođe "
"možete podesiti koje se fascikle koriste."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:2142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders Dialog Screenshot"
msgstr "Snima dijaloga fascikli."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save to HTML file"
msgstr "Sačuvaj u HTML fajl:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Save to file selector allows you to decide where you want to save your "
"image gallery html page."
msgstr ""
"Birač fajlova u kome određujete gde ćete sačuvati HTML stranicu načinjene "
"galerije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recurse subfolders"
msgstr "Rekurzivno kroz potfascikle"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Recurse subfolders check box enables recursing of subdirectories. If the "
"check box is enabled, a slider and spin box are enabled to select the "
"recursion depth."
msgstr ""
"Ovom kućicom aktivirate rekurziju kroz potfascikle. Ako je kućica popunjena, "
"aktiviraju se klizač i brojčanik za izbor dubine rekurzije."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy original files"
msgstr "Kopiraj izvorne fajlove"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Copy original files check box creates an image folder storing copies of "
"the original images used in the gallery."
msgstr ""
"Ovom kućicom zadaje se stvaranje fascikle u koju treba kopirati izvorne "
"slike sadržane u galeriji."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:2172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use comment file"
msgstr "Upotrebi fajl sa komentarima"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The use comment file check box enables a file selector to choose a comments "
"file to use with your gallery. The comment file contains the subtitles for "
"the images."
msgstr ""
"Ova kućica poziva birač fajlova radi zadavanja fajl sa komentarima za "
"galeriju. Fajl sa komentarima sadrži podnaslove slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2175
#, no-c-format
msgid "The format of this file is:"
msgstr "Format ovog fajla je:"

# literal-segment: FILENAME\w+
# literal-segment: ИМЕФАЈЛА\w+
#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:2176
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
