#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It brings up a simple dialog box where you can enter a file name using the "
"wild card characters * and ?, for example entering <literal role=\"extension"
"\">*.html</literal> will select all files ending with <literal role="
"\"extension\">.html</literal> while <filename>?a*</filename> will select all "
"files which have the letter a as the second character in their filename."
msgstr ""
"Doziva jednostavan dijalog u kome upisujete obrazac imena fajla, sa "
"džokerskim znakovima * i ?. Na primer, unos <literal role=\"extension\">*."
"html</literal> izabraće sve fajlove koji se završavaju sa <literal role="
"\"extension\">.html</literal>, dok će <filename>?a*</filename> izabrati "
"imena fajlova koja imaju slovo „a“ na drugom mestu."

